fields.question: What is EPF contribution?
fields.matched_response: Employee EPF contributions (8%) are deductible. Employer contributions (12%) are not taxable. Withdrawals are generally tax-exempt upon retirement.

fields.question: How is rental income taxed?
fields.matched_response: Rental income is taxed under investment income. A 25% standard deduction is allowed for maintenance before tax is applied on the net income.

fields.question: What is personal relief?
fields.matched_response: Personal relief is an annual allowance of Rs. 1,800,000 that reduces your taxable income. It applies to all resident individuals.
